                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>Bailey continued to face hardships after leaving the home of his stepmom and dad, like the unexpected death of his older sister. But he persevered, eventually becoming the first person in his family to graduate high school before continuing his education.&lt;/p>&#xa;"
